*root-5.12.00e-r1 (16 Oct 2006)
  16 Oct 2006; Sebastien Fabbro <seb@ist.utl.pt> 
  +root-5.12.00e-r1.ebuild
  -root-5.12.00e.ebuild
  Fixed libafterimage dep, added odbc flag, xrootd disable with
  gcc>4.1. Fix bug when both qt3 and qt4 are installed.
	
*root-5.12.00e (12 Sep 2006)

